<div class="content-page">
  <p class="page-intro">Clean Arcade is a collection of free browser games with no ads, no tracking, and no accounts. Just open a game and play.</p>

  <div class="about-grid">
    <div>
      <h2>Why we built this</h2>
      <p>Most game sites are built to extract attention. Pop-ups, autoplay videos, cookie walls, forced sign-ups. We wanted a place where you could just play a game without fighting through all that.</p>
      <p>Every game on Clean Arcade runs directly in your browser. Nothing to download, nothing to install, nothing to sign up for.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2>Your data stays with you</h2>
      <p>Game progress, high scores, and favorites are saved in your browser's local storage. We never see it. There are no accounts, no analytics, and no tracking scripts anywhere on this site.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2>Built by</h2>
      <p>Clean Arcade is designed and developed by <a href="https://www.pikespeakwebdesigns.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pikes Peak Web Designs</a>.</p>
    </div>

